      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I told him that everyone is crying for him. New York is crying for him. America is crying for him. We all are.''</p>
        <p>IMAM MUSA KABBA, on Moussa Magassa, who lost five children in a Bronx fire. [B5]</p>
